3
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:37,680
I'm heading out now.

4
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,199
Take care on the road.

5
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:39,919
Alright.

6
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:40,319
You head back.

7
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:01,840
Brothers,

8
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:03,360
This time, Liu Heihu

9
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,560
I've finally put him in his place.

10
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,800
He's completely tamed now.

11
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,479
Hua'er,

12
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:08,520
Third Brother,

13
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:09,680
