18
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,919
You two little rats planning to betray us?

19
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,520
Little White Horse,

20
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,479
We've made up our minds.

21
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:37,680
We're going down the mountain to fight the Japs.

22
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,960
Fight the Japs.

23
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:45,960
