30
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:40,560
You’re close with my brothers.

31
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,279
They all treat you well.

32
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,319
Because you saved their lives.

33
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:45,480
Right?

34
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,199
But Hua,

35
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:51,600
There’s an order to these things.

36
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:54,639
I’ve saved their lives too.

37
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,839
And they’ve saved mine.

38
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,399
